            "type": "TextBlock",
            "text": "The political reaction phase landed Monday night with The Reload's roundup of statements from across the gun-policy ecosystem. NRA-ILA called the package the biggest one-day regulatory overhaul in the agency's history; SAF welcomed the pistol-brace rescission; Brady, Everytown, Giffords, Moms Demand opposed.",
